results.deck: Zombie Studios are a video games developing company who mainly develop on the Unreal Engine for all platforms. Zombie released Blacklight: Tango Down on XBLA on Wednesday, July 7 2010. Blacklight is a multiplayer only first-person-shooter. It was later released on PS3 and PC.
